just_use wiki.go

# label: SPIKE
# spike: SIDECAR_WIKI
# role: supports feature — browser-based read-only wiki for repo docs + sidecars + source

SIDECAR_WIKI V1 (2026-04-15). Serves the repo as a read-only wiki
at `/gopher/wiki/...`. Landing = README.md rendered. Tree browsing
at `/gopher/wiki/tree/*`. Markdown rendered via goldmark; everything
else shown as preformatted text.

Security: path resolved against repo root (cwd at server start),
rejects any path that escapes via `..`.

Expected to evolve: comments, search, anchored feedback. Promote
to WORKHORSE once stable; drop the SIDECAR_WIKI tag at that point.
